ence should be addressed implies that the disturbed community composition may persist for many years at this station. Full recovery .is likely to require more than 5 yr and may take a decade or more. An effort to evaluate the accumulated monetary loss to fishery from the accident indicates that direct costs of shoreline cleanup and vessel damage were considerably greater.},
